org.wattdepot.common.domainmodel

Class MeasurementRateSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wattdepot.common.domainmodel.MeasurementRateSummary

  • public class MeasurementRateSummary
extends Object
    MeasurementRateSummary a summary of the Measurements created by a given Sensor in a Depository. This class breaks down the time intervals to the last minute, last fifteen minutes, last hour and last day.
    Author:
    Cam Moore
